Package communication.messages.objects

Class ExtractorEntities

  • java.lang.Object
    • communication.messages.objects.ExtractorEntities
  • public class ExtractorEntities
extends java.lang.Object
    The ExtractorEntities class is used to extract all objects, which are subclasses of Entities in case they are stored in an EntitiesArray. This class solves two parsing problems: first entities are abstract and cannot be instantiated, second the Entities class is to general (information from subclasses may get lost). (This class only exists for gson/json parsing)
    Author:
    Matthias Ruf, Sarah Engele
